<h2 id="so-what-is-meta-box-exactly">So what is Meta Box, exactly?</h2>

<p>Meta Box is a simple yet powerful plugin that helps developers build custom meta boxes and custom fields in WordPress fast and easily.</p>

<p>The plugin lets you define custom meta boxes and custom fields via arrays and handles everything behind the scene automatically. It has a wide range of field types, field settings and supports not only post meta but also term meta, user meta, comment meta, settings pages and custom tables.</p>

<h2 id="contribution">Contribution</h2>

<p>Like Meta Box plugin, this documentation is <a href="https://github.com/wpmetabox/docs">open sourced on Github</a>. The website is powered by Jekyll and the content is written in Markdown.</p>

